Package: bskernel
Title: Flexible Auto-covariance Construction via Spline Kernels
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lachlan", "Astfalck", , "lachlan.astfalck@uwa.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8369-9384"))
Description: This package provides flexible auto-covariance kernel construction via inverse Fourier transforms of B-spline bases, as well as some handy tools for optimisation. It accompanies the paper ''Universal approximation of auto-covariance functions via spline kernels''.
